Package edu.umn.cs.csci3081w.project.model

Class Line

java.lang.Object
edu.umn.cs.csci3081w.project.model.Line
public class Line extends Object
Represents a transportation line in the simulation. A Line consists of an outbound and inbound route, and can be associated with either buses or trains depending on its type.
